maLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-olympic-delegation-departs-for-paris/00000190-dae7-dc1d-a5d1-ffff214f0000</guid></item><item><title>自加沙战争爆发以来，以色列寻求心理健康帮助的士兵人数大幅增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/health/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-sees-major-spike-in-soldiers-seeking-mental-health-help-since-gaza-war-started/00000190-dadb-d548-a3ba-fedb3a6c0000</link><description>纳塔尔创伤求助热线报告称，因担心自杀而接到的电话数量增加了六倍，并且增加了 145%</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 15:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/health/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-sees-major-spike-in-soldiers-seeking-mental-health-help-since-gaza-war-started/00000190-dadb-d548-a3ba-fedb3a6c0000</guid></item><item><title>据警方称，巴勒斯坦人涉嫌在约旦河西岸的家中谋杀以色列监狱看守</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-suspected-in-murder-of-israeli-prison-guard-according-to-police/00000190-da8a-dab4-afb9-fbeaef3b0000</link><description>奥弗监狱的一名雇员 Yohai Avni 被发现身上多处被刺伤。警方相信凶手还试图放火烧他的家。在工作中，阿夫尼与安全囚犯和哈马斯恐怖分子接触</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 14:30:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-suspected-in-murder-of-israeli-prison-guard-according-to-police/00000190-da8a-dab4-afb9-fbeaef3b0000</guid></item><item><title>巴黎奥运会开幕前几天，法国议员表示“不欢迎”以色列代表团</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/days-before-paris-olympics-begin-french-lawmaker-says-israeli-delegation-not-welcome/00000190-da8a-dab4-afb9-fbea45740000</link><description>法国外交部长称这位极左翼议员的言论“不负责任且危险”，随后表示欢迎以色列人。尽管采取了前所未有的安全措施，以色列仍将派遣创纪录数量的辛贝特特工来保护其代表团</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 14:06:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/days-before-paris-olympics-begin-french-lawmaker-says-israeli-delegation-not-welcome/00000190-