ousands-flee-as-officials-report-37-dead/00000190-d9fd-dab4-afb9-fbfd409b0000</link><description>由于以色列国防军袭击哈马斯目标，该市东部社区的居民被要求暂时撤离到安全区</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 12:01:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/israel-launches-offensive-in-gazas-khan-yunis-thousands-flee-as-officials-report-37-dead/00000190-d9fd-dab4-afb9-fbfd409b0000</guid></item><item><title>美国共和党的“2025计划”已在以色列成为现实</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/project-2025-is-already-the-reality-in-israel/00000190-d99f-d566-adfa-fbbf81a50000</link><description>共和党的游戏计划将把美国转变为一个民族主义、宗教独裁国家。以色列政府的行动呼应了美国蓝图的许多部分</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 11:38:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/project-2025-is-already-the-reality-in-israel/00000190-d99f-d566-adfa-fbbf81a50000</guid></item><item><title>解释：谁是也门胡塞武装？他们为何攻击以色列？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-07-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/explained-who-are-the-houthis-and-why-are-they-attacking-israel/0000018b-a4da-da24-a1cb-b7de6c5f0000</link><description>尽管位于以色列以南 2000 公里处，胡塞运动目前仍对特拉维夫发动了致命的无人机袭击，并对度假城市埃拉特发动了数次袭击。专家解释了为什么这符合其更广泛的反以色列、反犹太议程，以及为什么它更像是赞助人伊朗的合作伙伴而不是代理人</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 09:58:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-07-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/explained-who-are-the-houthis-and-why-are-they-attacking-israel/0000018b-a4da-da24-a1cb-b7de6c5f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在与拜登关系破裂、以色列公众骚动之际启程前往华盛顿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-departs-to-washington-amid-tattered-relations-with-biden-israeli-public-uproar/00000190-d957-d548-a3ba-ffdf191f0000</link><description>总理将于周三在国会联席会议上发表讲话，一些民主党人表示将抵制这次会议，而另一些人则发誓要扰乱会议；内塔尼亚胡定于周二与拜登会面</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 09:39:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-departs-to-washington-amid-tattered-relations-with-biden-israeli-public-uproar/00000190-d957-d548-a3ba-ffdf191f0000</guid></item><item><title>战争将会结束，但数月乃至数年后，加沙人仍将继续死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-war-will-end-but-gazans-will-continue-to-die-many-months-and-years-later/00000190-d51f-dd40-ab95-f79fdb2d0000</link><description>癌症患者得不到治疗； 36 家医院中有 26 家停止运营；大部分水不能饮用，污水流淌在街道上。这些只是一些因素，即使在达成停火协议后，加沙人的健康状况仍前景黯淡</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 09:12:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-war-will-end-but-gazans-will-continue-to-die-many-months-and-years-later/00000190-d51f-dd40-ab95-f79fdb2d0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：辛瓦尔在 10 月 7 日之前就“囚犯问题上的冲突”警告以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/report-sinwar-warned-israel-before-oct-7-about-a-flare-up-over-the-prisoners/00000190-d93f-d566-adfa-fb3f602d0000</link><description>根据以色列的评估，加沙哈马斯领导人指的是与囚犯和失踪人员有关的事态发展，而不是袭击</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 08:06:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/report-sinwar-warned-israel-before-oct-7-about-a-flare-up-over-the-prisoners/00000190-d93f-d566-adfa-fb3f602d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对也门的袭击：战术上的成功暴露了战略上的失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-strike-on-yemen-a-tactical-success-that-exposes-a-strategic-failure/00000190-d5c1-dd26-af91-ffffbbe30000</link><description>以色列飞行员飞那么远去轰炸也门的一个港口，这证明了其对伊朗这个真正的、更近的威胁的威慑力是多么有限。责任归咎于总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡，他对伊朗核威胁的痴迷意味着他忽视了其代理人的危险</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 06:40:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/israels-strike-on-yemen-a-tactical-success-that-exposes-a-strategic-failure/00000190-d5c1-dd26-af91-ffffbbe30000</guid></item><item><title>网络噩梦：哈马斯拥有数千名以色列士兵和家庭的详细情报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/hamas-produced-detailed-dossiers-on-over-2-000-israeli-air-force-soldiers-families/00000190-d737-d548-a3ba-ffff22810000</link><description>哈马斯针对 2000 多名印度空军士兵（其中包括一些身居敏感岗位的士兵）创建的详细报告中包含了身份证件、电话号码、银行详细信息、车牌，在某些情况下甚至包括密码</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 03:57:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/hamas-produced-detailed-dossiers-on-over-2-000-israeli-air-force-soldiers-families/00000190-d737-d548-a3ba-ffff22810000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡继续发出混合信号，以色列国防官员推动加沙协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-officials-press-for-hostage-deal-within-weeks-as-pm-sends-mixed-signals/00000190-d65e-d548-a3ba-fede58710000</link><description>国防部官员一致认为，费城路线并不是该协议的主要障碍；拜登退出总统竞选对人质谈判的影响还有待观察；胡塞武装对以色列可能发动的袭击保持高度戒备</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 03:07:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-officials-press-for-hostage-deal-within-weeks-as-pm-sends-mixed-signals/00000190-d65e-d548-a3ba-fede58710000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军证实，几个月前，两名以色列人质在加沙哈马斯的囚禁中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article-live/israeli-delegation-led-by-mossad-chief-to-depart-for-hostage-talks-in-qatar-on-thursday/00000190-d84c-dc1d-a5d1-fd5f1b4c0000</link><description>以色列南部发生未遂刺伤袭击 ■ 加沙医疗消息称，以色列国防军对汗尤尼斯的袭击造成 37 名巴勒斯坦人死亡 ■ 以色列国防军表示，从黎巴嫩进入以色列后拦截了多个空中目标，没有人员伤亡报告 ■ 摩萨德负责人率领的以色列代表团将启程前往以色列参加人质谈判卡塔尔周四</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 02:59:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article-live/israeli-delegation-led-by-mossad-chief-to-depart-for-hostage-talks-in-qatar-on-thursday/00000190-d84c-dc1d-a5d1-fd5f1b4c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方预计也门战区将变得更加中心化，可能会再次袭击胡塞武装目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-expects-yemen-theater-to-become-more-central-may-strike-houthi-targets-again/00000190-d733-de6f-abb2-dfbfddb80000</link><description>空军的调查发现，空中管制人员发现了在特拉维夫造成一人死亡的无人机六分钟，但由于没有将其视为威胁而没有被击落 ■ 军方加强了防空，特别是在南部地区</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 22:21:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-expects-yemen-theater-to-become-more-central-may-strike-houthi-targets-again/00000190-d733-de6f-abb2-dfbfddb80000</guid></item></channel></rss>